Class WhanauWireNetwork

  • java.lang.Object
    • peersim.dynamics.WireGraph
      • it.unitn.disi.ds2.whanau.controls.WhanauWireNetwork
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    peersim.core.Control

    public class WhanauWireNetwork
extends peersim.dynamics.WireGraph
    This class implements the methods used to create the network topology. It can easily generate a random topology of given size or it can build a network given a pre-defined topology (like the graph of a social network.)
